metadata.name: Yawn
metadata.description: This is a photograph of a tiger taken at Bandhavgarh National Park , Madhya Pradesh , India . I was waiting for a tiger near a small dam area in the park . Continuous Alarm calls were given by other animals like monkeys , Deer etc which is confirm sign a existence of a tiger in nearby area . A beautiful frame in my mind and i was praying that tiger should sit at a place near to a hut constructed by forest department . After waiting of almost 1 hour tiger came and sat at the desired place which converted into this beautiful image .
